{"id": 1909, "genre": 1000, "title": "看多了综艺节目，你都能识别哪些“drama”套路？", "description": "当我们在讨论“综艺效果”的时候，我们都在讨论些啥？（题图来自：Pixabay)", "record_count": 21039, "comment_count": 39, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/201709150621026bxqXHhopvnaL4YE.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 1, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2017-09-17T17:00:09Z", "questions": [{"id": 2972, "title": "看多了综艺节目，你都能识别哪些“drama”套路？", "content": "现在人们都如何滥用了“综艺效果”or drama？", "genre": 2, "options": [{"id": 235535, "content": "演技浮夸，跳出平铺直叙的正常人设定，比如暴脾气主厨每集喷火300次训队员", "image": "img/option/option/20170914183848ktd0TjJlDQhgVKy4.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 235536, "content": "卖人设，比如数学不好、音痴、游戏黑洞、生活不能自理.....", "image": "img/option/option/20170914231822n5GtdAKXuW42gIc8.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 235537, "content": "打感情牌，演恋爱，相爱相杀的友谊温情满满，通力合作的热情和团结", "image": "img/option/option/20170914223132fWTHS81EKRmLVNGy.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 235538, "content": "情商低当成耿直，“我涉世未深不会说话你别往心里去啊”", "image": "img/option/option/20170914225002Jp3N9c6QdhwOIT2q.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 235539, "content": "极端化，日常生活里一个明星的“公主心”指数是10，节目里硬拗到100", "image": "img/option/option/20170914231759t1XCjWJRHLhsvpGd.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 235540, "content": "虚假的矛盾冲突，互相攻击，最后安排握手言和", "image": "img/option/option/20170914230207hpirnmycdUA1X89z.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 236199, "content": "别有用心的剪辑，为了突出互撕而压缩正常内容时间，明星被骂上热门", "image": "img/option/option/20170917213846UmQfxXiVaHMjhqIK.jpeg", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 236200, "content": "参赛选手或者明星动不动就“不玩了”“退赛”“把机会让给需要的人”", "image": "img/option/option/20170917214220N37bKps2lvHt8Cjw.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 235541, "content": "节目用后期花字放大情绪，去旅行看看夕阳就是想家，做菜多干了点活就是爱护小辈", "image": "img/option/option/201709141844530AwSTbNGfL7jiOdc.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}]}]}